  <brief_title>The Study of Mechanism of Alzheimer's Disease Using Acupuncture Based on fMRI</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Study of Brain Functional Network Modulatory Mechanism of Alzheimer's Disease Using Acupuncture at the &quot;Four-gate&quot; Acupoints</official_title>
